## Supporting maps under the main view
::::

::::: submap-grid
::: submap-card
### Crime counts by neighborhood

Counts reflect reported incidents in the rolling 30-day window.

```{r}
make_summary_map(
  site_data$crime_neighborhoods,
  value_col = "crime_count",
  title = "30-day crime count",
  palette = site_config$palette$crime_fill,
  value_format = format_number_label
)
```
:::

::: submap-card
### Declared permit value by neighborhood

Permit totals emphasize where the largest declared work value is currently concentrated.

```{r}
make_summary_map(
  site_data$permit_neighborhoods,
  value_col = "value_sum",
  title = "30-day permit value",
  palette = site_config$palette$permit_fill,
  value_format = format_currency_label
)
```
